Usage: addMimCap [-help] -cell <string> [-orient <string>] [-prefix <string>] [{-stepX <float> -stepY <float>} [-area {x1 y1 x2 y2}]] [{-area {x1 y1 x2 y2} | -loc {x y}}] [-loc {x y} | -offset {x y}]

-help                                # Prints out the command usage
-area {x1 y1 x2 y2}                  # area (box, required)
-cell <string>                       # cell name (string, required)
-loc {x y}                           # location (point, required)
-offset {x y}                        # offset (point, optional)
-orient <string>                     # orientation (string, optional)
-prefix <string>                     # prefix name (string, optional)
-stepX <float>                       # step size in X (float, optional)
-stepY <float>                       # step size in Y (float, optional)